            "notes": "The deck revolves around utilizing aggressive creatures, burn spells, and disruption to overwhelm the opponent and control the battlefield. It includes a mix of powerful sorceries and instants, along with creatures with abilities that can help push through damage or disrupt the opponent's strategy. The commander, Deadpool, Trading Card, adds an extra layer of versatility and interaction to keep the opponent off balance. The mana base is designed to provide consistent access to the necessary colors for spells and abilities. Overall, the deck aims to apply constant pressure on the opponent while disrupting their game plan to secure a quick victory in a one-on-one format."
